eedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 30, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104atz1665702722835.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/atz1665702722835.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/atz1665702722835.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"atz1665702722835\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Handle ProcScript modification functions as in previous versions.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"atz1665702722835__topic_d141563e1_d141564e1_d141565e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"atz1665702722835__p_d141566e1_d141567e1_d141568e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$MOD_VERSION</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <code class=\"ph codeph\">V5.2</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">V6.1</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">V7.1</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">V7.2</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"atz1665702722835__section_lnz_zfr_2wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1018746e75\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16925e1_d16926e1_d16927e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Any application assignment file</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"atz1665702722835__section_nhf_1gr_2wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1018746e121\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"atz1665702722835__p_d141575e1_d141576e1_d141577e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$MOD_VERSION</span> allows you to specify\n        that the values of the ProcScript modification functions <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occmod</span>,\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formmod</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formdbmod</span>, and\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldmod</span> should be determined as they were in previous versions of\n        Uniface. The options <code class=\"ph codeph\">V6.1</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">V7.1</code> are equivalent; both\n        options are present to increase the documentation value of your assignment file.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"atz1665702722835__note_e4l_2gr_2wb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The <code class=\"ph codeph\">$MOD_VERSION</code> setting provides a\n        short-term solution for compatibility problems caused by the changes in the modification\n        functions between versions. You are encouraged to adapt your applications to the current\n        behavior as quickly as possible.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"atz1665702722835__p_d141578e1_d141579e1_d141580e1\">For the functions <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occmod</span>,\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formmod</span>, and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formdbmod</span>, the table summarizes how\n        each of the options available with <code class=\"ph codeph\">$MOD_VERSION</code> affects the values. (The\n        function <code class=\"ph codeph\">$occdbmod</code>, which was introduced in V7.2, is included for\n        completeness.)</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"8\" id=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Results of $occmod, $formmod, $occdbmod, and $formdbmod for different types of\n          fields</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" colspan=\"2\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__1\"></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" colspan=\"3\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__2\"> $occmod / $formmod </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" colspan=\"3\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__3\"> $occdbmod / $formdbmod </th>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__4\"> Field is ... </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__5\"> Entity is ... </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__6\"> V5.2 </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__7\"> V6.1 / <p class=\"p\">V7.1</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__8\"> V7.2 </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__9\"> V5.2 </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__10\"> V6.1/ <p class=\"p\">V7.1</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__11\"> V7.2 </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__1 atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__4\" rowspan=\"2\"> Database </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__1 atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__5\"> Updatable, database </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__2 atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__6\"> 1 / 1 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__2 atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__7\"> 1 / 1 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__2 atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__8\"> 1 / 1 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__3 atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__9\"> — / 1 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__3 atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__10\"> — / 1 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__3 atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__11\"> 1 / 1 </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__1 atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__5\"> Non-updatable, database </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__2 atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__6\"> 1 / 1 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__2 atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__7\"> 1 / 1 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__2 atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__8\"> 1 / 1 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__3 atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__9\"> — / 1 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"atz1665702722835__table_d16928e1_d16929e1_d16930e1__entry__3 atz